HEADWORD: Entrochal
<hw>En"tro*chal</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Pertaining to, or
consisting of, entrochites, or the joints of encrinites; -- used of a
kind of stone or marble.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Entrochite</ent>⟦br⟧
